# 🚀 Day 21 – Digital Privacy Dashboard with Claude AI

## 📌 Overview

On **Day 21** of the **60 Days Claude AI Challenge**, I explored how AI can be used to analyze and visualize digital privacy using an interactive dashboard.

Using the provided prompt and sample dataset, I generated a **Digital Privacy Dashboard** that evaluates an individual's digital footprint, privacy exposure, online risks, company data exposure, and privacy improvement opportunities.

The dashboard presents complex privacy insights through interactive visualizations, helping users better understand their online presence and take informed steps toward improving digital security.

